44124092701, \"text\": \"Mexican\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\"}, {\"begin\": 2189, \"end\": 2196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9999999953734005, \"rank\": 4.494429123552947e-09, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}, {\"begin\": 2294, \"end\": 2304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9999999984925125, \"rank\": 1.5073981359221282e-09, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the cheek\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2217}, {\"ngram\": \"some big swings\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2255}, {\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2284}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, all five judges saw it differently and awarded the Mexican the round which meant Richardson's dream of reaching the Olympic final was over and he admitted afterwards that he felt he won what was a tight contest.\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2527, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2367, \"end\": 2374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"score\": 0.5580509032060591, \"rank\": 0.6448244124092701, \"text\": \"Mexican\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\"}, {\"begin\": 2397, \"end\": 2407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9999999984925125, \"rank\": 1.5073981359221282e-09, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all five judges\", \"from\": 2316, \"to\": 2331}, {\"ngram\": \"the round\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2384}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic final\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2445}, {\"ngram\": \"a tight contest\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: \\\"It was close, it was a close bout.\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2574, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a close bout\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2573}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's hard to say really if I am happy, I am a bit disappointed with my performance but what I will say is I am proud of myself about how I have conducted myself throughout this tournament.\", \"from\": 2575, \"to\": 2763, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my performance\", \"from\": 2643, \"to\": 2657}, {\"ngram\": \"this tournament\", \"from\": 2747, \"to\": 2762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have been ultra-professional and I hope that I have represented the country with pride and honour because I have done my best.\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 2894, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 2843}, {\"ngram\": \"pride\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2854}, {\"ngram\": \"honour\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 2865}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So I hope the country are happy and proud of what I have achieved because although I have lost tonight I have managed to bring a bronze medal home.\", \"from\": 2896, \"to\": 3044, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 2907, \"to\": 2918}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze medal home\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3043}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I certainly did feel like I won the bout, but I am certainly not screaming a robbery because it's close and it's far too soon to say anything like that.\", \"from\": 3046, \"to\": 3199, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bout\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3087}, {\"ngram\": \"a robbery\", \"from\": 3122, \"to\": 3131}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 3180, \"to\": 3188}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me he was a good opponent, seeded number two in the tournament and I am happy with my performances this week.\\\"\", \"from\": 3201, \"to\": 3316, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good opponent\", \"from\": 3216, \"to\": 3231}, {\"ngram\": \"number\", \"from\": 3240, \"to\": 3246}, {\"ngram\": \"the tournament\", \"from\": 3254, \"to\": 3268}, {\"ngram\": \"my performances\", \"from\": 3289, \"to\": 3304}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT Have your say... 1 Crime Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping 2 Football Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news 3 UK Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war 4 Lifestyle Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026 Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026 5 Football Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 3318, \"to\": 4196, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3378, \"end\": 3387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.8805856445571822, \"rank\": 0.13556227112060806, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\"}, {\"begin\": 3478, \"end\": 3487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.8805856445571822, \"rank\": 0.1355